# AI-Resume-Screening-System
An intelligent AI-powered Resume Screening System designed to automate candidate shortlisting using Machine Learning and Natural Language Processing (NLP). This project analyzes resumes, extracts important skills, matches candidates with job requirements, and ranks applicants based on relevance and qualification. 
